Computer Graphics Class at the Baylor University https://www.baylor.edu/

Final project

Author: antonin smid

The base for this project was written using tutorial series by ThinMatrix.
The water material is created based on ThinMatrix's tutorial.
https://www.patreon.com/thinmatrix

This project uses libraries:

Lightweight Java Game Library https://www.lwjgl.org/
https://sourceforge.net/projects/java-game-lib/files/Official%20Releases/LWJGL%202.9.1/lwjgl-2.9.1.zip/download

Slick https://github.com/ariejan/slick2d/tree/master/src/org/newdawn/slick
Fast Noise library https://github.com/Auburns/FastNoise_Java
OpenGL v3.2

